### Employee API Test File
### Use this with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools

@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001/api/employeesapi

### Get all employees
GET {{baseUrl}}

###

### Get employee by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

###

### Create new employee
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "title": "Software Engineer",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com"
}

###

### Update employee
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "title": "Senior Software Engineer",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

###

### Delete employee
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/2

###

### Search employees by last name
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?lastname=Doe

###

